             <span id="ctl00_MainContentHolder_lblDescription">
              <p>
               Anyone looking for serious equipment of proven quality will be pleasantly surprised by
               <strong>
                Swarovskis ATS/STS HD Spotting Scopes
               </strong>
               . These spotting scopes provide unbeatable value, durability, and a light-weight modular design which easily and affordably accommodates upgrades. Whether you want to start with a
               <strong>
                65mm objective lens
               </strong>
               and upgrade to a whopping
               <strong>
                95mm objective lens
               </strong>
               , the
               <strong>
                Swarovski ATS/STS HD Spotting Scope
               </strong>
               series allows for such upgrades without buying an entirely new body. Revolutionary design, outstanding performance and a wide range of choices make the ATS/STS a leader in the world of
               <strong>
                spotting optics
               </strong>
               .
